OL,3,CRugby player's father to receive
OL,4,C#100,000 over false social media claims
OL,6,FThe father of Paddy Jackson is to be
OL,7,Fawarded #100,000 in libel damages for
OL,8,Ffalse claims he tried to pay off the
OL,9,Fcomplainant at the rugby star's rape
OL,10,Ftrial, a judge ruled today.
OL,12,FPeter Jackson secured the payout
OL,13,Fagainst reality TV personality
OL,14,FDanielle Meagher over the lies she
OL,15,Fposted on social media.
OL,17,FDelivering judgment at the High Court
OL,18,Fin Belfast, Master Mark Harvey
OL,19,Finsisted there must be consequences
OL,20,Ffor her "vile" allegations.
