OL,3,CRugby player's father to receive
OL,4,C#100,000 over false social media claims
OL,6,F"There seems to be a sense in some
OL,7,Fquarters that there is an online cloak
OL,8,Fof invisibility leading people to type
OL,9,Fthings on a keyboard they may never
OL,10,Futter in person," he said.
OL,12,F"Such cowardly online bile causes real-
OL,13,Flife hurt and upset to other people
OL,14,Fand damages their reputation.
OL,16,F"The message needs to be out there
OL,17,Fthat when someone posts baseless and
OL,18,Flibelous accusations online, the
OL,19,Frepercussions can be very serious."
