OL,3,CRugby player's father to receive
OL,4,C#100,000 over false social media claims
OL,6,FMr Jackson, 69, declared himself fully
OL,7,Fvindicated by the outcome in his seven
OL,8,Fand a half year defamation battle.
OL,10,F"My family and I have suffered a
OL,11,Fconstant barrage, and it's still not
OL,12,Ftoo late for an apology for these
OL,13,Ffalse accusations," he said.
OL,15,FHe sued Ms Meagher, also known as
OL,16,FDanielle Collins, over the bogus
OL,17,Fallegations published on Twitter, now
OL,18,Frebranded as X, back in April 2018.
