OL,6,FWeeks previously former Ireland and
OL,7,FUlster rugby players Paddy Jackson,
OL,8,F33, and Stuart Olding, 32, had been
OL,9,Funanimously acquitted of raping the
OL,10,Fsame woman.
OL,12,FBoth sportsmen denied any criminal
OL,13,Fwrongdoing throughout their high-
OL,14,Fprofile trial in Belfast.
OL,16,FJudgment was previously obtained
OL,17,Fagainst Ms Meagher when she failed to
OL,18,Fenter an appearance in the case.
