OL,6,FAt a further hearing earlier this
OL,7,Fmonth Mr Jackson and his wife Gay
OL,8,Frevealed he has been left "crushed" by
OL,9,Fthe fake claims he bribed a witness
OL,10,Fand attempted to bribe the complainant
OL,11,Fat their son's trial.
OL,13,FThe court heard he became so obsessed
OL,14,Fand paranoid that he suffered a stroke
OL,15,Fearlier this year while trawling the
OL,16,Finternet to check on Ms Meagher's
OL,17,Flatest postings.
