OL,6,FHis loss of self-confidence since the
OL,7,Ftweets were published left him
OL,8,Fsocially withdrawn and close to a
OL,9,Frecluse.
OL,11,FThe retired sales manager described it
OL,12,Fas a pre-planned attack on his
OL,13,Fintegrity.
OL,15,F"This was an absolute statement that I
OL,16,Fhad been criminally dishonest," he
OL,17,Ftold the court.
