OL,3,CRugby player's father to receive
OL,4,C#100,000 over false social media claims
OL,6,F"If the intent of the tweets was to
OL,7,Fget into my brain and into my heart
OL,8,Fthat was achieved by the individual
OL,9,Fwho put them out there."
OL,11,FIn his evidence Mr Jackson recalled
OL,12,Fbeing "knocked for six" when the
OL,13,Ftweets were posted just as the family
OL,14,Fwere trying to help their son rebuild
OL,15,Fhis rugby career following the not
OL,16,Fguilty verdict.
OL,18,FMs Meagher later denied knowing
OL,19,Fanything about the tweets, making
OL,20,Fbaseless claims the account was
OL,21,Foperated by a talent agency.
