OL,6,FDespite her non-appearance, Mr Jackson
OL,7,Fsaid he would have loved to meet her
OL,8,Fface to face for an explanation.
OL,10,FHe likened the ordeal and her approach
OL,11,Fto the case of a boxer taking repeated
OL,12,Fblows in the ring.
OL,14,FWhile he constantly trawled social
OL,15,Fmedia to see if the lies had been
OL,16,Fspread further, Gay Jackson told the
OL,17,Fcourt she tried to ignore the tweets
OL,18,Fby "burying her head in the sand".
