OL,6,FShe said her husband became so
OL,7,Fparanoid about what others thought of
OL,8,Fhim that he became increasingly
OL,9,Fdistrustful and withdrew from social
OL,10,Foccasions.
OL,12,FShe also described the shock when he
OL,13,Fsuffered a stroke in August this year
OL,14,Fwhile in bed checking on any reviews
OL,15,Fabout the defendant at the Edinburgh
OL,16,FFringe Festival.
OL,18,F"It crushed him and the confidence he
OL,19,Fhad in himself," Mrs Jackson stated.
