OL,6,F"His whole confidence and self-esteem
OL,7,Fhas been ripped from him because of
OL,8,Fwhat happened."
OL,10,FRuling on the scale of damages, Master
OL,11,FHarvey called the tweets a personal
OL,12,Fattack aimed at trashing someone's
OL,13,Freputation with false accusations of
OL,14,Fcriminal dishonesty.
OL,16,FHe said it was rare to encounter such
OL,17,Fextensive efforts to track down a
OL,18,Fdefendant, including serving notice on
OL,19,Faddresses in the USA and enlisting a
OL,20,Fprivate security firm to try to locate
OL,21,Fher in Dublin.
