OL,6,F"There is no mitigation, there has
OL,7,Fonly been aggravation, evasion and
OL,8,Fdoubling down on the allegations by
OL,9,Fthe defendant," Master Harvey held.
OL,11,F"The lesson for the defendant, and
OL,12,Ffrankly for those posting on social
OL,13,Fmedia platforms generally, is that
OL,14,Fvirtual comments have real-life
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,17,F"It is her egregious comments and
OL,18,Fsubsequent conduct that have led to
OL,19,Fthis."
