OL,6,FAwarding Mr Jackson #100,000 in
OL,7,Fdamages plus legal costs, he
OL,8,Frecognised it may not be
OL,9,Fstraightforward to recover
OL,10,Fcompensation from someone living
OL,11,Foverseas.
OL,13,FMaster Harvey added: "Even if this
OL,14,Fshould prove to be a paper judgment,
OL,15,Fwhich would be a regrettable outcome,
OL,16,Fat the very least the plaintiff can
OL,17,Fsay he brought his case, obtained
OL,18,Fjudgment and he has been vindicated,
OL,19,Fwhich will hopefully avoid any repeat
OL,20,Fof such vile allegations."
