OL,10,F"This is a damning judicial critique
OL,11,Fof the defendant's response to our
OL,12,Fclient's litigation," the lawyer said.
OL,14,F"Even at this very late stage and
OL,15,Farmed with a #100,000 judgment Mr
OL,16,FJackson is still prepared to give her
